<h4>Genesys Care Mobile App</h4>
<br/>
 
<p>The Genesys Care Mobile Application is intended to help you interact with Genesys more quickly and efficiently. Using your hand-held device, you will be able to:</p>

<ul>
    <li>Review your Open Cases (Support and Admin), including all public Case Updates</li>
    <li>Post updates to your Cases</li>
    <li>Contact any of our regional Customer Care Centers</li>
    <li>Chat with the Owner of your Support Case (PureEngage Premise and PureCloud only)</li>
    <li>Request for Escalation (PureEngage and PureCloud cases only) and Case Closure</li>
    <li>View Alarms in your environment (Requires Remote Alarm Monitoring - PureEngage Premise only)</li>
</ul>

<p>Please note that the mobile app is only available to customers and partners that have My Support Designated Contact or Read-Only access.</p>

